WEBVTT

01:48.960 --> 01:49.880
It's you?

01:51.800 --> 01:52.960
It's me.

01:55.080 --> 01:55.960
We meet again,

01:58.680 --> 02:00.040
old friend.

02:22.960 --> 02:24.560
You once told me

02:25.600 --> 02:28.000
that besides the Spirit-Binding Ring
on your hand,

02:29.920 --> 02:31.600
the other half of the Spirit-Storing Jade

02:32.320 --> 02:34.320
had been sealed
inside the Mist-Blood Cave,

02:35.160 --> 02:38.480
the most treacherous,
perilous place in the world.

02:39.240 --> 02:40.680
One wrong step,

02:41.440 --> 02:43.360
and you'd die without a trace.

02:44.240 --> 02:45.240
But look.

02:46.360 --> 02:48.560
I still went there, took the jade,

02:49.160 --> 02:51.000
and turned it into a magical artifact.

02:57.080 --> 02:58.320
Pretty, isn't it?

02:59.760 --> 03:01.600
You're going to such lengths

03:01.680 --> 03:03.560
to obtain the Dragon Deity's Power.

03:05.280 --> 03:06.640
What exactly is that for?

03:08.000 --> 03:10.440
I don't believe you're only acting
on Jiu Ying's orders.

03:12.040 --> 03:13.200
What for?

03:17.520 --> 03:19.160
Naturally,

03:24.200 --> 03:27.320
to drag you down
from that hollow divine throne.

03:39.440 --> 03:40.320
Ji Ling!

03:43.560 --> 03:44.640
Stay.

04:00.840 --> 04:02.640
Don't force me to use
Word Magic on you again.

04:05.120 --> 04:07.000
My power may be weaker than yours,

04:08.680 --> 04:11.880
but I'm on guard against you
every second now.

04:11.960 --> 04:13.000
It won't be that easy

04:14.240 --> 04:15.400
for you to control me.

05:02.320 --> 05:03.360
Shiguang.

05:08.600 --> 05:09.680
Shiguang.

05:10.320 --> 05:11.400
Shiguang.

06:20.640 --> 06:21.960
Wu Shiguang?

06:38.320 --> 06:39.480
Wu Shiguang.

06:42.320 --> 06:43.520
Wu Shiguang.

06:45.160 --> 06:46.000
Wu Shiguang.

06:51.720 --> 06:54.520
It's all right. I'm right here.

07:02.600 --> 07:05.240
I… I…

07:05.760 --> 07:07.080
You don't have to say anything.

07:10.200 --> 07:11.280
I understand.

07:13.120 --> 07:13.960
I…

07:17.400 --> 07:18.520
I'm just…

07:19.480 --> 07:21.760
a little tired.

07:22.960 --> 07:23.960
I want you to stay…

07:25.800 --> 07:26.920
with me.

07:32.880 --> 07:36.120
Why didn't you leave earlier?

07:36.920 --> 07:38.760
I'm blind.

07:39.800 --> 07:41.520
Where could I have gone?

07:54.320 --> 07:56.040
It's so cold here.

07:58.720 --> 08:00.680
I want to go home.

08:05.560 --> 08:06.520
I'm afraid

08:07.800 --> 08:08.880
we won't

08:09.640 --> 08:11.440
get the Star Stone after all.

08:16.560 --> 08:17.880
It's all right.

08:19.680 --> 08:21.400
At least Wu Shiguang

08:22.560 --> 08:24.160
has left

08:27.120 --> 08:28.400
safely.

08:32.520 --> 08:33.559
Do you remember?

08:35.320 --> 08:38.120
You still owe me a favor.

08:39.799 --> 08:41.080
How about this?

08:41.600 --> 08:42.720
Grant me one request after we get out.

08:43.760 --> 08:44.680
All right.

08:53.120 --> 08:55.240
Go ahead. Whatever it is,

08:56.240 --> 08:57.480
I promise I'll do it.

08:59.120 --> 09:00.280
I'll do it.

09:02.640 --> 09:03.560
Don't…

09:04.800 --> 09:08.240
Don't hate me.

09:43.640 --> 09:44.480
Why isn't it working yet?

09:59.800 --> 10:00.680
It worked!

10:01.520 --> 10:03.480
Lucky us. Now we can save them.

10:04.080 --> 10:05.120
Let's go.

10:13.640 --> 10:14.680
What happened?

10:15.200 --> 10:16.280
Is this discrimination against demons?

10:32.560 --> 10:35.200
With lustrous light,
let all evil be undone!

11:14.760 --> 11:16.200
Good thing I got sent here.

11:16.280 --> 11:17.800
Had it been the skinny Hua Qi instead,

11:17.880 --> 11:19.760
he wouldn't have been able to carry you.

11:22.520 --> 11:24.000
Open up!

11:24.080 --> 11:26.160
Open up! Open up!

11:26.240 --> 11:28.280
I'm still out here! Open up!

11:36.200 --> 11:37.680
Master… Master Xi?

11:55.520 --> 11:56.360
Father?

11:56.960 --> 11:57.920
Chi, get back.

11:58.680 --> 11:59.760
That isn't Xie Lingxi.

12:00.800 --> 12:01.840
That's Jiu Ying.

12:04.360 --> 12:06.280
How did Jiu Ying turn into Master Xi?

12:07.720 --> 12:08.720
Before Xie Lingxi died,

12:09.400 --> 12:12.360
he left behind the last of his power
in his own tombstone

12:12.440 --> 12:14.440
to protect Wu Shiguang.

12:14.960 --> 12:17.480
But unexpectedly, his great power

12:18.000 --> 12:20.040
also drew in Jiu Ying's spirit fragment.

12:20.840 --> 12:23.080
Who would've thought? After 1,000 years,

12:23.960 --> 12:27.280
I still got the chance
to take root in the Star Stone.

12:29.000 --> 12:30.480
All these years,

12:31.000 --> 12:32.600
those double-flower hunters

12:32.680 --> 12:34.720
have destroyed so many
of my spirit fragments.

12:34.800 --> 12:36.040
Despicable.

12:36.120 --> 12:39.360
And now they've
delivered themselves right to my door.

12:40.600 --> 12:42.720
I'll let them all die in there.

13:08.400 --> 13:09.360
Father.

13:13.960 --> 13:16.120
Father, what do we do?

13:17.640 --> 13:18.480
I can't beat him.

13:20.120 --> 13:21.440
Don't give up.

13:21.520 --> 13:24.120
Stop making a fool of yourselves here.

13:24.640 --> 13:26.760
The Star Stone is about to shatter.

13:27.400 --> 13:30.880
They'll be trapped inside forever.

13:31.960 --> 13:33.320
Even a tiny ant

13:33.920 --> 13:35.920
can bring down
a mighty dragon or elephant.

13:36.800 --> 13:38.200
Even a mayfly

13:38.720 --> 13:41.120
can shake a towering tree.

13:42.760 --> 13:44.120
Chi,

13:44.840 --> 13:46.440
do you remember our family motto?

13:48.480 --> 13:49.760
"Do your best."

13:51.920 --> 13:53.160
I know

13:54.520 --> 13:57.280
that even though you say it all the time,

13:58.320 --> 14:00.280
you've never truly lived by it.

14:01.880 --> 14:03.040
But today,

14:04.280 --> 14:05.840
I will teach you what it really means

14:06.440 --> 14:08.600
to do your best.

14:09.400 --> 14:12.680
This fire striker
is the sacred artifact of the weasel clan.

14:12.760 --> 14:14.720
Its name is Ember.

14:16.440 --> 14:19.600
If it senses that you truly mean
to give everything you've got,

14:19.680 --> 14:20.800
it will unleash a power

14:21.400 --> 14:22.960
that can burn through anything.

14:34.160 --> 14:37.520
Weasels should crawl back
into their holes.

15:28.560 --> 15:31.640
No!

15:33.920 --> 15:35.080
Father!

15:35.800 --> 15:37.320
Wonderful, Father!

15:38.320 --> 15:40.080
You were amazing. You beat Jiu Ying.

15:40.160 --> 15:42.480
Our clan is finally going to be famous.

15:42.560 --> 15:43.600
We've produced a great hero.

15:45.040 --> 15:46.120
This is such an honor.

15:48.320 --> 15:49.360
What's wrong?

15:50.320 --> 15:51.360
You silly child,

15:52.360 --> 15:54.080
after today, no one will beat you

15:55.640 --> 15:56.720
ever again.

15:58.160 --> 16:00.320
-Have you forgotten the family motto?
-No, I haven't.

16:00.840 --> 16:01.800
Didn't you fail to do your best?

16:01.880 --> 16:04.040
-I… I really did try my best.
-You…!

16:07.040 --> 16:08.600
Father. Father, what's wrong?

16:13.120 --> 16:14.440
Good boy,

16:17.000 --> 16:18.520
I hope you'll keep

16:20.080 --> 16:22.000
your feet on the ground,

16:23.280 --> 16:24.920
take everything seriously,

16:26.600 --> 16:28.640
-and always do your best.
-Father…

16:28.720 --> 16:29.800
Father, get up.

16:29.880 --> 16:32.640
I'll take you to Wu Shiguang.
He has the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:32.720 --> 16:34.600
He can save you, Father!

16:35.480 --> 16:36.520
Father!

16:40.040 --> 16:41.040
Father!

16:41.880 --> 16:42.880
Father…

16:49.680 --> 16:50.760
Father!

16:50.840 --> 16:52.080
Father…

17:03.440 --> 17:04.400
Father…

17:18.599 --> 17:19.720
Father…

17:21.480 --> 17:22.599
I promise…

17:23.599 --> 17:25.560
I promise I'll do my best.

17:25.640 --> 17:26.520
Father…

17:27.720 --> 17:29.400
I'll never be like that again.

17:30.040 --> 17:31.080
Father…

17:31.160 --> 17:33.280
-<i>Remember.</i>
-I promise…

17:33.360 --> 17:35.760
-<i>No matter what you are</i>
-Father, I promise…

17:35.840 --> 17:37.520
-<i>or how capable you are,</i>
-Father…

17:38.400 --> 17:41.960
<i>always give it everything</i>
<i>you've got and do your best.</i>

17:42.920 --> 17:45.320
<i>Only then can you live with no regrets.</i>

18:43.440 --> 18:44.280
You Chi.

18:50.840 --> 18:53.640
I… I don't have a father anymore.

19:04.000 --> 19:05.880
We're out of the illusion now.

19:05.960 --> 19:07.360
Why is he still unconscious?

19:07.960 --> 19:09.160
Take him back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:09.800 --> 19:11.120
I'll examine him there.

19:16.040 --> 19:17.560
I already put the fragment in my pouch.

19:18.520 --> 19:21.760
Why can my artifact
still sense Jiu Ying's evil aura?

19:22.480 --> 19:23.680
Let's take them back
to the Shilin Sect first.

19:24.280 --> 19:26.000
Once we turn in these two
spirit fragments of Jiu Ying's,

19:26.720 --> 19:27.600
there will only be

19:28.440 --> 19:30.160
three left in the world.

19:30.240 --> 19:33.440
But those last three
still haven't been detected at all.

19:33.520 --> 19:34.360
What a headache.

19:41.000 --> 19:42.680
We're taking Commander Li
back to the Shilin Sect first.

19:43.600 --> 19:44.480
You Chi,

19:45.240 --> 19:47.800
your father was a hero.

19:48.320 --> 19:50.040
He saved all our lives.

19:52.640 --> 19:53.720
Take care.

20:12.080 --> 20:13.080
Shiguang.

20:16.680 --> 20:17.960
You again?

20:30.200 --> 20:31.200
Master.

20:33.200 --> 20:34.400
You've grown up.

20:41.120 --> 20:42.960
This is only a trace of power

20:43.040 --> 20:44.680
I left behind to protect you.

20:46.120 --> 20:47.600
I can't hold this human form for long.

20:48.520 --> 20:49.680
Protect me?

20:56.160 --> 20:57.720
So you've been protecting me all along.

20:59.400 --> 21:02.120
No wonder Wu Shiguang
always manages to escape danger.

21:02.200 --> 21:04.400
It was thanks to your protection

21:05.640 --> 21:06.800
that I wasn't killed

21:07.320 --> 21:09.600
by the curse on that beast trap.

21:10.800 --> 21:11.840
Am I right?

21:14.040 --> 21:16.320
No wonder it only worked
with Wu Shiguang's blood.

21:17.960 --> 21:19.640
As you probably know now,

21:20.800 --> 21:22.520
my hands were once stained with blood.

21:24.640 --> 21:26.200
Among the blood of sinners,

21:26.720 --> 21:27.960
mine is there too.

21:30.600 --> 21:31.920
I, too, was one of the guilty.

21:40.840 --> 21:43.320
All the memories I had
when I was alive are stored inside.

21:43.840 --> 21:46.760
My blood resonates with my true form

21:47.360 --> 21:49.800
and awakens the memories buried within.

21:50.800 --> 21:51.880
And that

21:52.400 --> 21:55.680
accidentally dragged all of you
into my memories.

21:56.720 --> 21:59.480
Master, in the Star Stone illusion,

22:00.000 --> 22:02.600
you said you promised Chi Wen

22:02.680 --> 22:04.480
you'd protect someone for him.

22:07.800 --> 22:09.040
Who was it?

22:12.640 --> 22:14.080
You already know the answer,

22:15.960 --> 22:16.840
don't you?

22:22.320 --> 22:23.560
He asked you to look after me

22:24.280 --> 22:25.320
and guide me.

22:26.520 --> 22:28.440
Was it because he felt guilty
after slaughtering

22:29.080 --> 22:30.520
the flood dragon clan?

22:33.840 --> 22:35.320
Didn't you see the truth

22:36.800 --> 22:38.480
in the illusion?

22:39.600 --> 22:41.040
Chi Wen wasn't the one

22:41.960 --> 22:43.360
who slaughtered the flood dragons.

22:45.600 --> 22:47.240
The culprit

22:48.440 --> 22:50.400
was always searching
for a dragon's descendant.

22:55.200 --> 22:56.240
I…

22:59.440 --> 23:01.120
Am I Chi Wen's child?

23:01.200 --> 23:02.680
Of course not.

23:04.840 --> 23:06.080
You are his younger brother.

23:07.840 --> 23:11.000
You are the Tenth Dragon Son.

23:17.560 --> 23:18.680
Shiguang,

23:19.520 --> 23:23.520
you remember the dragon-scale birthmark
on your chest, right?

23:26.120 --> 23:28.360
Before the Nine Dragons
sacrificed themselves

23:29.360 --> 23:32.560
and transformed into a vast mountain range
to seal Jiu Ying away,

23:33.240 --> 23:35.920
each of them removed
their most precious reverse scale.

23:36.440 --> 23:37.680
Those scales fused together

23:38.200 --> 23:39.640
and became the Dragon Stone.

23:40.720 --> 23:42.720
I stood watch
as that Dragon Stone gave birth.

23:44.720 --> 23:45.960
And so you came into being.

23:46.880 --> 23:48.320
You are the world's

23:50.160 --> 23:51.440
tenth dragon.

23:55.000 --> 23:56.040
I'm a dragon?

23:57.800 --> 23:59.200
Ever since the flood dragons
were wiped out,

23:59.800 --> 24:01.000
for all these decades,

24:01.840 --> 24:04.920
I've spent every day and night
training in the spells you taught me.

24:40.560 --> 24:42.480
My hatred for dragons
was what kept me going,

24:43.800 --> 24:46.040
dragging out this painful life.

24:48.880 --> 24:50.000
And now, after all this time,

24:52.640 --> 24:54.280
you're telling me

24:54.360 --> 24:55.680
I'm a dragon?

24:57.200 --> 24:58.600
I'm a dragon?

25:04.240 --> 25:06.080
So the flood dragons weren't
wiped out because of Chi Wen.

25:11.720 --> 25:12.960
It was because of me!

25:28.560 --> 25:30.520
Even I didn't realize

25:30.600 --> 25:32.680
those Shilin Sect hunters

25:33.400 --> 25:35.280
were actually Jiu Ying in disguise.

25:37.000 --> 25:38.120
I thought the Dragon Deity…

25:42.480 --> 25:43.520
Chi Wen?

25:46.720 --> 25:47.880
What about him?

25:49.680 --> 25:50.560
Nothing.

25:51.880 --> 25:52.840
Master,

25:55.960 --> 25:57.960
why didn't you tell me sooner?

25:59.600 --> 26:00.480
Shiguang,

26:02.480 --> 26:05.280
your birth was tied to a heavy duty
from the start.

26:06.280 --> 26:09.320
I wanted you to have

26:10.760 --> 26:12.000
a carefree childhood

26:12.080 --> 26:14.320
before you learned the truth.

26:15.160 --> 26:16.640
I never expected

26:16.720 --> 26:18.960
your identity would bring disaster
to the flood dragons.

26:22.200 --> 26:23.640
The Dragon Deity's Power

26:23.720 --> 26:26.600
has already begun
entering your body, hasn't it?

26:29.560 --> 26:30.560
His body?

26:31.920 --> 26:35.240
Isn't the Dragon Deity's Power
stored in the prayer beads?

26:35.320 --> 26:36.640
Of course not.

26:38.960 --> 26:40.200
First the scales.

26:40.840 --> 26:42.080
Then the claws.

26:42.160 --> 26:43.560
Then the horns.

26:44.480 --> 26:45.760
And finally, the eyes.

26:46.280 --> 26:49.160
Each time one share of
the Dragon Deity's Power enters your body,

26:49.240 --> 26:50.600
a petal-shaped scale mark

26:50.680 --> 26:53.080
will appear on your forehead.

26:54.560 --> 26:55.760
It is the sign

26:56.680 --> 26:59.080
that you're gradually becoming a dragon.

26:59.680 --> 27:01.600
Once you gather all four shares
of the Dragon Deity's Power,

27:02.120 --> 27:03.800
you'll become a true dragon.

27:03.880 --> 27:05.040
Then,

27:06.200 --> 27:08.160
you'll naturally understand everything.

27:08.960 --> 27:11.840
For now, let me give you a hand

27:11.920 --> 27:14.760
in obtaining the second share
of the Dragon Deity's Power.

27:55.760 --> 27:57.360
Will he end up like Xiaowei?

27:58.600 --> 28:00.280
Once the Dragon Deity's Power
leaves the body,

28:01.400 --> 28:02.920
there's no turning back.

28:37.520 --> 28:38.520
Old friend,

28:39.440 --> 28:40.280
I'm here.

28:45.480 --> 28:46.560
I did it.

28:48.480 --> 28:49.720
The Star Stone is whole again,

28:50.560 --> 28:51.440
and it's shining again.

28:52.040 --> 28:53.640
Can you free my clansmen

28:54.240 --> 28:55.760
from petrification now?

29:00.520 --> 29:01.640
I can't.

29:04.480 --> 29:05.600
Do you still hate me?

29:18.680 --> 29:21.480
You were born the Star Stone
with the whole world in your heart.

29:23.080 --> 29:25.080
But because of me,

29:25.160 --> 29:27.600
the world came to see you as evil.

29:27.680 --> 29:28.800
You should hate me.

29:28.880 --> 29:30.320
I'm a sinner.

29:36.000 --> 29:36.960
But please,

29:38.200 --> 29:39.160
save my clansmen.

29:40.040 --> 29:43.040
<i>They're innocent.</i>
<i>They're in too much pain.</i>

29:59.800 --> 30:01.040
I've never hated you.

30:03.680 --> 30:05.040
I just can't do it.

30:06.520 --> 30:09.920
The petrification spell
cannot be reversed.

30:10.000 --> 30:11.760
Since ancient times,

30:12.680 --> 30:14.120
that has always been the case.

30:16.120 --> 30:17.200
That's impossible.

30:19.440 --> 30:20.840
That's impossible.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.840
Master Chi Wen told me

30:23.360 --> 30:24.800
to find the Star Stone.

30:24.880 --> 30:26.560
As long as the Star Stone
still exists in this world,

30:26.640 --> 30:28.040
there is still hope.

30:28.120 --> 30:29.120
Find the Star Stone,

30:29.200 --> 30:32.760
undo the petrification,
and make amends for your sins.

30:32.840 --> 30:34.280
He said

30:35.160 --> 30:37.000
the Star Stone could save my clansmen.

30:37.760 --> 30:39.720
I asked Chi Wen to say that.

30:42.000 --> 30:42.920
Back then,

30:44.000 --> 30:45.680
you imprisoned yourself
in the Blackwater River.

30:46.880 --> 30:48.280
Your will had collapsed.

30:48.800 --> 30:50.160
All you wanted was to die.

30:51.080 --> 30:52.440
So I thought

30:53.240 --> 30:54.880
that maybe if you had hope,

30:55.880 --> 30:57.640
you'd keep living.

31:01.880 --> 31:02.880
I understand now.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.840
You kept lying to Wu Zhiqi,

31:06.800 --> 31:07.800
saying you hated him,

31:08.800 --> 31:10.280
but really,

31:10.880 --> 31:13.600
you were afraid that once he learned
that petrification couldn't be undone,

31:13.680 --> 31:15.840
he would lose the will to live.

31:16.360 --> 31:18.600
You chose to die

31:18.680 --> 31:20.520
so Wu Zhiqi could keep living.

31:25.080 --> 31:25.920
Master…

31:26.920 --> 31:29.360
Hope is like a tree
that grows in the Ruined Sand.

31:31.520 --> 31:33.000
<i>Take the Crying Elm for example.</i>

31:34.000 --> 31:37.560
<i>Though it takes root</i>
<i>deep in scarred and battered soil,</i>

31:38.640 --> 31:41.680
<i>its branches still climb toward the light.</i>

32:02.120 --> 32:03.280
<i>Only with hope</i>

32:04.280 --> 32:06.760
<i>can dead wood put out branches again.</i>

32:08.920 --> 32:10.120
<i>Hope is also like a seed.</i>

32:11.280 --> 32:12.960
<i>It needs time to grow</i>

32:14.000 --> 32:15.640
<i>and time to heal.</i>

32:18.120 --> 32:19.880
<i>When winter passes,</i>

32:21.200 --> 32:23.960
-<i>reunion will come.</i>
-Xizai?

32:29.040 --> 32:30.880
But what you gave me

32:34.320 --> 32:35.520
wasn't a seed.

32:36.720 --> 32:38.880
It was a lifeless stone.

32:39.600 --> 32:41.720
That's why I've come
to tell you the truth.

32:42.920 --> 32:45.120
The grudges of these past centuries

32:46.000 --> 32:47.480
should come to an end now.

32:52.560 --> 32:53.400
Bai Ze,

32:54.840 --> 32:56.600
I have one final wish.

32:58.040 --> 32:59.960
Please ask Master Dragon Deity

33:02.560 --> 33:04.760
to destroy my petrified clansmen.

33:05.920 --> 33:07.080
Destroy them.

33:10.120 --> 33:11.440
Put them

33:13.000 --> 33:14.640
out of their misery.

33:22.200 --> 33:23.200
Old friend.

33:25.120 --> 33:26.120
Old friend…

33:54.840 --> 33:55.920
You old geezer.

33:57.360 --> 33:59.680
When we were drinking earlier,

34:01.400 --> 34:02.760
for one moment,

34:03.720 --> 34:06.640
I really felt like you were a friend
I could tell anything to.

34:13.360 --> 34:14.239
Master…

35:01.080 --> 35:02.120
Shiguang,

35:02.840 --> 35:06.160
you are the only one in this world
I still can't let go of.

35:06.240 --> 35:07.720
Though I am gone,

35:08.400 --> 35:09.800
the Star Stone remains.

35:10.320 --> 35:11.760
If you find yourself
in dire straits one day,

35:12.480 --> 35:14.040
it may yet help you once.

35:15.560 --> 35:16.920
But remember this.

35:17.000 --> 35:19.040
The Star Stone's power is too great.

35:19.120 --> 35:20.320
Do not use it rashly.

35:21.760 --> 35:22.760
Master…

35:35.840 --> 35:36.880
Stop.

35:52.120 --> 35:53.160
Yuan Wuhuo,

35:53.240 --> 35:56.400
your name was meant to be a blessing.

35:57.080 --> 36:00.160
But now, you have become Jiu Ying's pawn,

36:00.920 --> 36:02.720
bringing disaster upon the world.

36:04.360 --> 36:07.000
<i>Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi,</i>

36:07.080 --> 36:09.240
<i>driven by your manipulation,</i>

36:09.320 --> 36:11.880
<i>both walked down</i>
<i>a path of self-destruction.</i>

36:11.960 --> 36:13.480
Master Dragon Deity,

36:14.480 --> 36:15.720
you've got it wrong.

36:16.880 --> 36:19.160
My name is now Yuan Wuhuo.

36:19.880 --> 36:21.400
"Wuhuo" as in "to gain nothing."

36:22.400 --> 36:24.040
I've long come to a realization.

36:24.640 --> 36:28.360
Life is fleeting and filled
with every kind of suffering.

36:29.160 --> 36:33.440
Whatever one spends a lifetime chasing,
in the end, it all amounts to nothing.

36:33.520 --> 36:36.280
Only by no longer clinging
to gain and possession

36:36.360 --> 36:38.440
can one stop fearing loss.

36:39.080 --> 36:40.960
Only with neither loss nor gain

36:41.760 --> 36:44.760
can one remain true to one's real self.

36:47.280 --> 36:48.560
I never thought

36:50.400 --> 36:51.640
you would come back.

36:52.880 --> 36:54.320
You should never have returned.

37:58.960 --> 37:59.920
What is it?

38:00.960 --> 38:03.400
Are you starting to feel the strain?

38:04.440 --> 38:06.720
You don't have much
demon power left, do you?

38:16.320 --> 38:18.400
The water of the Blackwater River

38:18.480 --> 38:20.600
can absorb demon power.

38:21.120 --> 38:24.200
Wu Zhiqi imprisoned himself here back then

38:25.520 --> 38:27.040
because he wanted to die.

38:28.040 --> 38:29.120
So,

38:31.320 --> 38:33.160
that's why you lured me here on purpose.

38:33.960 --> 38:35.840
So many years have passed,

38:37.840 --> 38:40.040
but you're as unguarded as ever.

39:19.600 --> 39:22.240
<i>Wrathful sandstorm, grant me your power.</i>

40:09.120 --> 40:10.520
Dragon Deity's Power?
